1
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:11,000
[typing on cell phone]

2
00:00:12,791 --> 00:00:13,750
DAD: COMING HOME NOW?

3
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:15,208
[daughter] <i>I'm almost home.</i>

4
00:00:16,375 --> 00:00:18,416
[scribbling]

5
00:00:23,791 --> 00:00:25,000
[cell phones chimes]

6
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:27,625
WANG YU-CHING: I'M ALMOST HOME

7
00:00:27,708 --> 00:00:29,583
<i>Let's eat together when I get home.</i>

8
00:00:36,833 --> 00:00:38,625
- [eerie music playing]
- [screaming]

9
00:00:53,166 --> 00:00:56,250
OKAY! I'LL WAIT FOR YOU TO COME HOME
READ, 10:37 p.m.

10
00:00:56,333 --> 00:00:58,291
- [eerie music continues]
- [dialing]

11
00:00:58,375 --> 00:01:01,416
[cell phone ringing nearby]

12
00:01:07,041 --> 00:01:08,041
Yu-ching.

13
00:01:09,583 --> 00:01:10,583
Yu-ching.

14
00:01:10,666 --> 00:01:12,666
[suspenseful music playing]

15
00:01:15,166 --> 00:01:16,833
Yu-ching!

16
00:01:22,541 --> 00:01:24,708
AGENT FROM ABOVE

17
00:01:25,833 --> 00:01:28,041
THE GHOST FORGE

18
00:01:28,541 --> 00:01:30,875
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

19
00:01:32,250 --> 00:01:33,250
[door opens]

20
00:01:37,875 --> 00:01:39,375
It's you again.

21
00:01:40,916 --> 00:01:45,500
We've been waiting… for two juniors.

22
00:01:46,625 --> 00:01:47,708
Where's the captain?

23
00:01:47,791 --> 00:01:49,125
[low action music playing]

24
00:01:49,708 --> 00:01:50,833
The chief?

25
00:01:53,166 --> 00:01:56,125
I'm the one in charge. Let's have a chat.

26
00:01:56,208 --> 00:01:59,875
When was the last time you
and Heilung Hall had a turf war?

27
00:01:59,958 --> 00:02:03,041
[laughs] My client is engaged
in legal business.

28
00:02:03,125 --> 00:02:04,958
He has no connection with gangsters.

29
00:02:05,041 --> 00:02:07,041
[low action music continues]

30
00:02:08,666 --> 00:02:10,375
[officer] We have records here

31
00:02:10,458 --> 00:02:12,500
that since 2018,

32
00:02:12,583 --> 00:02:16,291
there have been three turf disputes,
and dozens of fights.

33
00:02:18,083 --> 00:02:19,916
My client is a shareholder.

34
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,500
He doesn't participate in operations,

35
00:02:22,583 --> 00:02:24,000
dealing with minor disputes.

36
00:02:24,083 --> 00:02:25,500
[Chang Min] Minor disputes?

37
00:02:25,583 --> 00:02:27,500
A bid worth almost 100 million

38
00:02:27,583 --> 00:02:32,166
was just won by Heilung Hall
moments before this massacre.

39
00:02:32,250 --> 00:02:33,541
Isn't that odd?

40
00:02:33,625 --> 00:02:35,500
[music fades]

41
00:02:38,083 --> 00:02:41,750
You can't catch the culprit
so you bully honest citizens instead.

42
00:02:42,666 --> 00:02:44,750
You're paid with taxpayers' money.

43
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:48,041
Do you know how much tax I paid last year?

44
00:02:48,625 --> 00:02:49,916
- Mr. Shen.
- Sir.

45
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,250
Take note.

46
00:02:52,166 --> 00:02:54,208
Next time I pay taxes,

47
00:02:54,291 --> 00:02:57,000
buy some dog food too to feed <i>them!</i>

48
00:03:07,416 --> 00:03:08,291
Sorry.

49
00:03:08,375 --> 00:03:09,500
Let's go, sir.

50
00:03:10,541 --> 00:03:12,708
DAUGHTER DIDN'T COME HOME
SO I WENT OUT LOOKING

51
00:03:12,791 --> 00:03:14,166
FOUND WANG YU-CHING'S BACKPACK

52
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:16,250
[somber music playing]

53
00:03:16,958 --> 00:03:20,083
Please, sir.
You must find my daughter Yu-ching.

54
00:03:20,666 --> 00:03:23,250
There's only the two of us. We…

55
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,458
only have each other.

56
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:26,750
Please.

57
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:29,625
[somber music continues]

58
00:03:30,708 --> 00:03:34,458
FOUND WANG YU-CHING'S BACKPACK IN LANE 48

59
00:03:34,541 --> 00:03:36,541
[whirring]

60
00:03:48,166 --> 00:03:50,583
[muffled cries]

61
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:57,833
[suspenseful music playing]

62
00:04:01,958 --> 00:04:04,083
[continues crying]

63
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:12,291
Please! No, don't.

64
00:04:13,083 --> 00:04:14,125
No!

65
00:04:19,666 --> 00:04:20,791
[panting and sobbing]

66
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,458
[suspenseful music intensifies]

67
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:06,083
[Chang Min] Shen-Lung Crown Prince
made a statement:

68
00:05:06,166 --> 00:05:08,541
"Chi-sha is very likely the mastermind.

69
00:05:08,625 --> 00:05:11,083
He promised him all sorts of powers

70
00:05:11,166 --> 00:05:15,166
in exchange for killing people,
and extracting their vital spirits."

71
00:05:18,541 --> 00:05:19,416
Vital spirits?

72
00:05:25,125 --> 00:05:27,625
Vital spirit is one of the three souls.

73
00:05:27,708 --> 00:05:29,958
The spirits of those who died unjustly

74
00:05:30,041 --> 00:05:32,833
can be magically refined
into malicious spirits.

75
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:37,916
At Heilung Hall, Chi-sha manipulated
these spirits to murder them.

76
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,416
No doubt Vasavatti is involved.

77
00:05:41,916 --> 00:05:43,083
Look at this.

78
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,750
Missing girl, Wang Yu-ching.

79
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:49,000
Evidence of Vasavatti
in the area where she disappeared.

80
00:05:49,875 --> 00:05:52,291
[dramatic music playing]

81
00:06:02,958 --> 00:06:04,750
WUMENG OCCULTIST KIDNAPPED WANG GIRL

82
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,500
Where did you get this?

83
00:06:13,083 --> 00:06:16,208
You should bear in mind
your tasks are not complete.

84
00:06:16,291 --> 00:06:17,416
Before I replace you,

85
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:20,458
Vasavatti wants
to invade this world again.

86
00:06:21,375 --> 00:06:22,250
[Chang Min sighs]

87
00:06:23,458 --> 00:06:25,125
[music fades]

88
00:06:25,208 --> 00:06:26,750
You're handling that?

89
00:06:26,833 --> 00:06:28,958
The Prince and I are dealing with it.

90
00:06:29,041 --> 00:06:31,916
This case is about human life,
so I will help you.

91
00:06:33,958 --> 00:06:34,958
Thanks.

92
00:06:35,875 --> 00:06:37,875
[breathes deeply]

93
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,875
There is something
I'd like your help with.

94
00:06:48,791 --> 00:06:51,458
We have a warrant
to search Liu Kuan-fu's house.

95
00:06:51,541 --> 00:06:54,458
If you're available,
I'd like you to go and take a look.

96
00:06:54,541 --> 00:06:56,291
Check it out for ghosts and stuff.

97
00:06:56,916 --> 00:06:58,916
[somber music playing]

98
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:05,500
I know he's a suspect
in setting fire to your family house.

99
00:07:05,583 --> 00:07:09,375
But Chao and I have worked hard to collect
all sorts of evidence against him.

100
00:07:09,458 --> 00:07:11,750
Hopefully, we'll soon be able
to put this scumbag--

101
00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:13,541
You're afraid I'll kill him.

102
00:07:17,458 --> 00:07:19,333
Your men will be there too.

103
00:07:19,833 --> 00:07:22,291
I'm atoning for my sins.

104
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:23,666
I can't add another.

105
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:25,750
[somber music continues]

106
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:40,083
[music fades]

107
00:07:42,291 --> 00:07:44,416
[Chang Min] Chao'll already be there.
We'd better hurry.

108
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,250
- [Han Chieh] Yeah.
- Han.

109
00:07:47,708 --> 00:07:49,458
Do you have a moment to talk?

110
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:56,750
Um…

111
00:07:57,875 --> 00:08:01,083
Is my brother still in Dongfeng Market?

112
00:08:03,541 --> 00:08:06,583
The Underworld Messenger
didn't come for him.

113
00:08:07,208 --> 00:08:08,583
He should still be here.

114
00:08:09,083 --> 00:08:12,958
Well, after you opened my third eye,
I still haven't seen him.

115
00:08:14,125 --> 00:08:15,250
I know.

116
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:16,875
You were both very close.

117
00:08:16,958 --> 00:08:18,166
[poignant music playing]

118
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:19,708
But for both your sakes,

119
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:22,666
you mustn't dwell in the past.

120
00:08:23,541 --> 00:08:28,208
It's possible he doesn't want to rekindle
your memories of that awful fire.

121
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,708
Um… and you?

122
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:33,666
You went down to see your parents,
didn't you?

123
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:35,000
Are they well?

124
00:08:38,583 --> 00:08:40,041
I can't face them.

125
00:08:40,125 --> 00:08:42,125
[poignant music continues]

126
00:08:49,541 --> 00:08:50,833
That's why…

127
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,875
family matters like this

128
00:08:54,375 --> 00:08:57,583
remind me of how much
we must treasure them.

129
00:08:58,083 --> 00:09:00,208
Because one day they'll be gone.

130
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:03,916
- I have many regrets.
- [sobs]

131
00:09:06,916 --> 00:09:08,625
Well, I'll be going.

132
00:09:08,708 --> 00:09:10,708
[poignant music continues]

133
00:09:16,083 --> 00:09:18,250
DONGFENG EATERY

134
00:09:24,583 --> 00:09:26,375
- Sis!
- Hmm?

135
00:09:26,458 --> 00:09:28,875
- You've worked enough. Come and eat.
- [laughs] Okay.

136
00:09:30,875 --> 00:09:32,250
Wow!

137
00:09:32,333 --> 00:09:34,166
Every day is something different.

138
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:36,958
- You're such a genius.
- Of course I am.

139
00:09:37,041 --> 00:09:39,375
How can I not be with a sister like you?

140
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:42,416
Hey! Don't pinch.

141
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:45,916
Just eat up,
and let me know what you think.

142
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,500
[both chuckle]

143
00:09:51,916 --> 00:09:55,291
You have a genius younger brother
making dinner for you every night.

144
00:09:55,375 --> 00:09:57,458
Do you know how lucky you are?

145
00:10:10,833 --> 00:10:12,833
[music fades]

146
00:10:15,916 --> 00:10:17,916
[siren wailing]

147
00:10:20,291 --> 00:10:22,666
[officer] All right, let's move.
Yep, in here.

148
00:10:28,291 --> 00:10:29,125
Holy shit.

149
00:10:30,250 --> 00:10:31,083
CID

150
00:10:31,166 --> 00:10:33,416
Why is Mr. Liu's house
full of wronged souls?

151
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[eerie music playing]

152
00:10:38,375 --> 00:10:40,875
- Captain, this is what we've found.
- Okay.

153
00:10:42,625 --> 00:10:45,375
Hey. We've searched everywhere,
but haven't found anything.

154
00:10:45,458 --> 00:10:47,833
[Chang Min] Chao, this place is spooky.

155
00:10:52,416 --> 00:10:54,500
TEMPLE FIRE, TWO DEATHS
ARSON LINKED TO LAND DISPUTE?

156
00:10:59,083 --> 00:11:00,083
[chuckles]

157
00:11:00,166 --> 00:11:02,166
[eerie music continues]

158
00:11:25,541 --> 00:11:26,666
What do you want?

159
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,041
To take his life.

160
00:11:28,958 --> 00:11:30,625
He caused my death.

161
00:11:33,708 --> 00:11:34,875
Black command.

162
00:11:35,375 --> 00:11:36,333
A token?

163
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:40,458
The Underworld permitted me.

164
00:11:40,541 --> 00:11:43,541
Wherever he goes, I go also.

165
00:11:44,458 --> 00:11:45,541
Those guys too.

166
00:11:52,875 --> 00:11:54,875
[eerie music continues]

167
00:11:59,291 --> 00:12:02,125
Hey, this place is pretty weird.

168
00:12:02,208 --> 00:12:03,708
[music fades]

169
00:12:03,791 --> 00:12:05,958
They all died because of Kuan-Fu.

170
00:12:06,833 --> 00:12:10,416
- They want revenge.
- Can't you help them cross over?

171
00:12:12,208 --> 00:12:13,833
They possess a token.

172
00:12:13,916 --> 00:12:17,541
An eye for an eye is forbidden,
but it's different in hell.

173
00:12:17,625 --> 00:12:20,208
A wronged soul can be avenged.

174
00:12:20,291 --> 00:12:21,541
Gods can't interfere.

175
00:12:23,666 --> 00:12:25,416
[Chao] All right, let's pack it up.

176
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,166
Let's go.

177
00:12:31,083 --> 00:12:33,291
[eerie music playing]

178
00:12:42,666 --> 00:12:46,250
DONGFENG MARKET

179
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,958
Uh, who is she?

180
00:12:54,583 --> 00:12:55,458
Why are you here?

181
00:12:56,041 --> 00:12:57,041
Oh.

182
00:12:58,333 --> 00:13:01,625
A while back, when I was
at the Third Crown Prince's temple,

183
00:13:01,708 --> 00:13:03,375
something strange happened.

184
00:13:03,458 --> 00:13:05,666
Someone died, but their soul wasn't there.

185
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:10,000
The Shen-Lung Prince has been caught,
and vital souls returned.

186
00:13:10,083 --> 00:13:11,625
I helped out too.

187
00:13:12,208 --> 00:13:13,958
Yeah, I heard all about it.

188
00:13:14,041 --> 00:13:15,750
That's why it's strange.

189
00:13:15,833 --> 00:13:18,791
And I checked for news from other temples.

190
00:13:19,375 --> 00:13:21,000
There are other missing souls.

191
00:13:22,833 --> 00:13:23,708
Go on.

192
00:13:23,791 --> 00:13:25,958
By my count, at least six.

193
00:13:26,041 --> 00:13:28,125
[tense music playing]

194
00:13:30,875 --> 00:13:32,833
Do you think the one behind it is…

195
00:13:33,791 --> 00:13:35,125
Chen Chi-sha?

196
00:13:37,708 --> 00:13:40,250
Yeah, but Chen Chi-sha
has already retired.

197
00:13:40,333 --> 00:13:42,916
- Why would he be behind it?
- This is Vasavatti.

198
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,916
[gasps] Oh.

199
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,833
Oh man, this is really bad.

200
00:13:48,916 --> 00:13:51,750
What's stopping the gods
getting rid of these demons?

201
00:13:51,833 --> 00:13:53,666
Why is this left up to you?

202
00:13:54,416 --> 00:13:55,250
Now, Miss.

203
00:13:55,333 --> 00:13:58,750
Gods can't get involved directly
in the Human Realm,

204
00:13:58,833 --> 00:14:00,666
especially with human problems.

205
00:14:02,166 --> 00:14:06,625
However, sometimes demons
want to use humans to do bad things.

206
00:14:06,708 --> 00:14:11,041
In that case, the gods send a message,
and their agent handles it.

207
00:14:12,041 --> 00:14:13,750
Is what makes me unlucky.

208
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,416
[eerie music playing]

209
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,333
And what happens if you lose to the demon?

210
00:14:23,458 --> 00:14:25,375
If I lose, I lose.

211
00:14:25,458 --> 00:14:26,625
[music fades]

212
00:14:26,708 --> 00:14:30,041
Hey, hey. Believe in yourself, okay?

213
00:14:30,125 --> 00:14:33,416
Hey, Chen Chi-sha has killed
so many people.

214
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,791
What, don't you care at all?

215
00:14:36,625 --> 00:14:37,875
[Han Chieh] I'm retiring soon.

216
00:14:37,958 --> 00:14:41,041
This demon requires
a more powerful god or agent.

217
00:14:41,625 --> 00:14:42,791
It's not my problem.

218
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:45,125
I can't believe this.

219
00:14:45,708 --> 00:14:48,125
Fine then. God, you're useless.

220
00:14:52,125 --> 00:14:53,125
[door closes]

221
00:15:04,208 --> 00:15:05,583
[gong]

222
00:15:05,666 --> 00:15:07,666
[grunting]

223
00:15:09,958 --> 00:15:11,958
[mysterious music playing]

224
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:18,208
[Han Chieh] Vasavatti appeared again.
Many people died, and yet you do nothing.

225
00:15:18,291 --> 00:15:22,500
You think this is a game,
and it's just a snap to fix things.

226
00:15:22,583 --> 00:15:24,833
There are rules that apply to gods.

227
00:15:24,916 --> 00:15:28,666
Those pesky fuddy-duddies up there
are very strict, you know.

228
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:31,708
If I make a random move
without their permission,

229
00:15:31,791 --> 00:15:34,166
then I'm violating the rules.

230
00:15:35,208 --> 00:15:39,166
Do you want me to end up like that monkey,
trapped under a mountain?

231
00:15:39,916 --> 00:15:42,958
Why can't gods
properly handle things like this?

232
00:15:43,041 --> 00:15:46,250
You have fighters
and other agents from above.

233
00:15:46,333 --> 00:15:49,750
A war between the demons and gods?

234
00:15:49,833 --> 00:15:53,708
It'd be catastrophic if we fight
in our true forms. The world ends.

235
00:15:54,958 --> 00:15:57,583
I think you guys just don't want
to get your hands dirty.

236
00:15:57,666 --> 00:15:59,041
But it's fine if we die.

237
00:16:02,291 --> 00:16:05,541
Are you afraid
of fighting Vasavatti again?

238
00:16:05,625 --> 00:16:06,750
[music fades]

239
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:08,583
[sighs]

240
00:16:09,166 --> 00:16:10,791
I know I don't have a choice.

241
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:14,166
- But I doubt I'll win.
- [chuckles]

242
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:18,958
Yeah, you're right.
He's well-prepared for it.

243
00:16:19,541 --> 00:16:20,500
Hmm.

244
00:16:20,583 --> 00:16:22,333
I don't think you'll win either.

245
00:16:23,166 --> 00:16:27,208
Hey. Aren't you meant
to provide me with encouragement?

246
00:16:27,291 --> 00:16:28,291
Oh.

247
00:16:29,166 --> 00:16:30,791
Then I'd be lying to you.

248
00:16:31,583 --> 00:16:36,708
Gods won't influence your free will.
Or tell you how to do things. [chuckles]

249
00:16:36,791 --> 00:16:38,958
[soft music playing]

250
00:16:39,041 --> 00:16:41,000
You're afraid of responsibility.

251
00:16:43,041 --> 00:16:45,416
If the outcome finally isn't good,

252
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:50,250
you can just shrug it off and say,
I made you do it.

253
00:16:54,375 --> 00:16:58,208
But don't forget,
for every task the gods bring,

254
00:16:58,958 --> 00:17:01,875
you have the right to decide
whether to accept.

255
00:17:03,458 --> 00:17:05,791
You can save all these souls.

256
00:17:06,583 --> 00:17:08,291
It all depends if you're willing.

257
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:15,083
You're a good-for-nothing brat.
That's what you are.

258
00:17:15,166 --> 00:17:16,958
[flames bursting]

259
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:19,250
Make your decision soon.

260
00:17:26,375 --> 00:17:28,250
[door opening]

261
00:17:28,333 --> 00:17:30,666
- [muffled screams]
- [suspenseful music playing]

262
00:17:39,416 --> 00:17:41,541
[continues crying]

263
00:17:43,625 --> 00:17:45,625
Shh.

264
00:17:50,708 --> 00:17:52,708
[suspenseful music continues]

265
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,208
[Zhang Min] I retrieved
all the surveillance footage

266
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:12,041
from near where Yu-ching went missing.

267
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:14,166
No trace of Chi-sha at all.

268
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:17,125
But if you extrapolate
from these crime locations,

269
00:18:17,208 --> 00:18:19,750
Chi-sha's whereabouts should be
in one of these three areas.

270
00:18:19,833 --> 00:18:20,666
12 DEAD, 1 KILLER

271
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:23,375
WANG YU-CHING,
HEILUNG HALL, SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

272
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:27,125
[man] <i>Someone died,</i>
<i>but their soul wasn't there.</i>

273
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:30,250
Other incidents have occurred elsewhere.

274
00:18:30,333 --> 00:18:32,083
Could also be Chi-sha.

275
00:18:32,791 --> 00:18:34,583
I'll check what area these were.

276
00:18:34,666 --> 00:18:36,666
[intriguing music playing]

277
00:18:38,833 --> 00:18:40,833
[groans softly]

278
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:44,916
What?

279
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:49,375
When you saw Kuan-fu,
did it stir the hatred in your heart?

280
00:18:49,458 --> 00:18:51,666
[music turns tense]

281
00:18:53,583 --> 00:18:54,583
It did.

282
00:18:55,666 --> 00:18:57,166
But I'll leave him to you.

283
00:18:57,750 --> 00:19:00,125
What if even the law can't deal with him?

284
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:04,625
He may escape the law, but not karma.

285
00:19:05,208 --> 00:19:07,250
So many would like to see him in hell.

286
00:19:07,333 --> 00:19:09,083
I'd need to get in the queue.

287
00:19:09,166 --> 00:19:10,375
[chuckles softly]

288
00:19:12,166 --> 00:19:13,083
Let's go.

289
00:19:32,625 --> 00:19:33,583
Hey.

290
00:19:34,375 --> 00:19:37,041
Go upstairs and bring me the tea cake.

291
00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:38,625
- I want to try it.
- [man] Yes, boss.

292
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:54,083
[dramatic music plays]

293
00:19:56,833 --> 00:19:58,625
It's this good?

294
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,375
[laughing] Mmm!

295
00:20:13,833 --> 00:20:15,500
[distorted laughs]

296
00:20:18,041 --> 00:20:19,708
[grunts]

297
00:20:30,708 --> 00:20:33,208
[dramatic music intensifies]

298
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:45,750
[calm music playing]

299
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,583
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

300
00:20:55,666 --> 00:20:57,166
[nervously] Officer Chao!

301
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:59,750
Oh, please! I want to confess.

302
00:20:59,833 --> 00:21:00,875
- Please.
- What?

303
00:21:00,958 --> 00:21:03,125
I want to confess. Lock me up.

304
00:21:03,208 --> 00:21:07,166
- [Chao] Mr. Shen, slow down and explain.
- I… I don't want to be bothered by ghosts.

305
00:21:07,250 --> 00:21:09,666
Please! I'm sorry!

306
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:11,875
I'm sorry. Please!

307
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,416
Leave me alone! I'll confess.

308
00:21:15,541 --> 00:21:19,458
- [panting] Officer Chao, save me.
- [suspenseful music playing]

309
00:21:19,541 --> 00:21:21,916
- The house of ghosts drove him crazy.
- Huh?

310
00:21:22,416 --> 00:21:25,708
Officer Chao, please. I'll admit
to everything, everything he did.

311
00:21:25,791 --> 00:21:27,291
I'll become a state witness--

312
00:21:27,375 --> 00:21:30,041
Mr. Shen, you'll lose your bar card
if you do that.

313
00:21:30,125 --> 00:21:31,750
What's more important than my life?

314
00:21:32,375 --> 00:21:35,291
Please. Save me, please. I'm begging you.

315
00:21:35,791 --> 00:21:37,791
[panting]

316
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:39,541
[eerie music playing]

317
00:21:39,625 --> 00:21:41,291
Tell us where Chi-sha is.

318
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:44,583
I know.

319
00:21:45,208 --> 00:21:47,791
I'll tell you everything.

320
00:21:51,583 --> 00:21:53,791
Hey, Han. You guessed right.

321
00:21:53,875 --> 00:21:57,000
Those ghosts drove him crazy.
He told us where Chi-sha is.

322
00:21:57,083 --> 00:21:58,833
I'm sending you the location.

323
00:21:58,916 --> 00:22:00,916
[eerie music builds]

324
00:22:25,416 --> 00:22:29,083
It's been a while, my old friend.

325
00:22:37,375 --> 00:22:39,083
[Han Chieh] Didn't you promise to retire?

326
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:42,750
And yet you're still
stealing vital spirits.

327
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:45,500
That girl, she's not here.

328
00:22:46,041 --> 00:22:48,375
There are many uses for Yu-ching.

329
00:22:48,875 --> 00:22:51,166
[eerie music continues]

330
00:22:51,875 --> 00:22:53,833
So she's with your new disciple?

331
00:22:56,083 --> 00:22:57,708
He's not my disciple.

332
00:22:59,125 --> 00:23:01,750
You're right. He's better than you.

333
00:23:01,833 --> 00:23:05,208
His magic has no scent.
Even I was deceived.

334
00:23:05,291 --> 00:23:07,791
He has two female ghosts.
One calls you uncle.

335
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:11,041
She said Vasavatti even threatened you.

336
00:23:11,666 --> 00:23:13,000
What's up with that?

337
00:23:19,291 --> 00:23:21,375
[distorted female voice] Save me.

338
00:23:21,458 --> 00:23:22,916
Save me.

339
00:23:23,958 --> 00:23:25,541
- Father?
- Uncle.

340
00:23:25,625 --> 00:23:27,083
- Save me.
- Please…

341
00:23:27,166 --> 00:23:29,291
- [Chi-sha] <i>Those two ghosts…</i>
- [red ghost] Save me.

342
00:23:29,375 --> 00:23:32,958
<i>The one in white is my niece.</i>
<i>The one in red is my daughter.</i>

343
00:23:33,541 --> 00:23:35,666
<i>Tien-chi exhumed their corpses,</i>

344
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:39,333
<i>and used Vasavatti's power</i>
<i>to control their souls,</i>

345
00:23:39,416 --> 00:23:41,166
<i>and turned them into malicious spirits.</i>

346
00:23:41,250 --> 00:23:43,791
Long time, Master Chen.

347
00:23:44,791 --> 00:23:47,333
- [eerie music continues]
- [scoffs]

348
00:23:47,416 --> 00:23:48,750
Why so cold?

349
00:23:48,833 --> 00:23:52,291
[Chi-sha] <i>They're threatening me,</i>
<i>monitoring my every move.</i>

350
00:23:52,375 --> 00:23:53,750
<i>And if I don't work with them,</i>

351
00:23:53,833 --> 00:23:58,041
<i>Tien-chi will let the souls</i>
<i>of these two girls dissipate.</i>

352
00:23:58,625 --> 00:24:00,000
Tien-chi?

353
00:24:01,125 --> 00:24:03,541
DEMON KING OF THE SIXTH HEAVEN
ENTICES MAN

354
00:24:06,375 --> 00:24:07,458
Five years ago,

355
00:24:07,541 --> 00:24:11,291
you promised me that if Vasavatti came
to you again, you'd tell me.

356
00:24:11,375 --> 00:24:13,000
[Chi-sha] So what if I did?

357
00:24:13,083 --> 00:24:16,291
If you hadn't stripped me
of my magical weapons,

358
00:24:16,375 --> 00:24:19,000
I wouldn't have turned out this way.

359
00:24:25,375 --> 00:24:28,500
As long as you prevail against
the Crown Prince's agent,

360
00:24:28,583 --> 00:24:31,416
your precious daughter and niece
will be free.

361
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,500
[dramatic music playing]

362
00:24:37,833 --> 00:24:39,166
[red ghost] <i>Father!</i>

363
00:24:40,916 --> 00:24:42,416
<i>Save me.</i>

364
00:24:43,083 --> 00:24:45,083
<i>Please, Father.</i>

365
00:24:59,875 --> 00:25:01,875
[music intensifies]

366
00:25:09,625 --> 00:25:10,625
[music fades]

367
00:25:11,791 --> 00:25:13,333
This is my karma.

368
00:25:13,958 --> 00:25:15,625
[breathes deeply]

369
00:25:15,708 --> 00:25:16,916
Vasavatti.

370
00:25:17,666 --> 00:25:18,875
He made you this.

371
00:25:19,458 --> 00:25:20,958
It's what I am.

372
00:25:22,416 --> 00:25:23,916
I'm unpardonable.

373
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:26,625
[celestial music playing]

374
00:25:26,708 --> 00:25:29,583
But those two girls
are innocent creatures.

375
00:25:34,333 --> 00:25:35,625
I'm not here to fight you today.

376
00:25:40,208 --> 00:25:44,375
He turned me into living death
to win against you.

377
00:25:45,625 --> 00:25:47,958
[music builds]

378
00:25:59,250 --> 00:26:00,125
[growling]

379
00:26:07,291 --> 00:26:09,125
[grunts]

380
00:26:11,333 --> 00:26:12,791
[action music playing]

381
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,000
[ghosts growl]

382
00:27:09,916 --> 00:27:11,166
Where's Yu-ching?

383
00:27:19,916 --> 00:27:21,416
I don't want to kill you.

384
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:23,916
You're saying that to a dead person.

385
00:27:24,541 --> 00:27:26,125
See you in hell.

386
00:28:14,333 --> 00:28:16,166
[groaning]

387
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:38,083
[drums play]

388
00:28:40,208 --> 00:28:42,208
[cries]

389
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:47,458
[theme music playing]

390
00:28:57,750 --> 00:29:00,500
Nine Dragons Fire Barrier?

391
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:13,125
[dragon roaring]

392
00:29:16,625 --> 00:29:18,625
[music stops]

393
00:29:43,250 --> 00:29:44,250
[groaning softly]

394
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:59,000
[tense music playing]

395
00:30:10,666 --> 00:30:12,791
[music turns eerie]

396
00:30:14,583 --> 00:30:16,791
I knew this day would come.

397
00:30:16,875 --> 00:30:18,500
[labored breathing]

398
00:30:21,375 --> 00:30:24,750
Full moon, magical formation, center.

399
00:30:27,291 --> 00:30:29,291
[music fades]

400
00:30:36,416 --> 00:30:38,416
[action music playing]

401
00:30:52,125 --> 00:30:53,125
[whistles]

402
00:30:56,041 --> 00:30:59,000
Master Chen. It's been a long road.

403
00:30:59,625 --> 00:31:01,625
[chuckles]

404
00:31:06,958 --> 00:31:09,083
DONGFENG MARKET

405
00:31:18,125 --> 00:31:20,125
[theme music playing]

406
00:32:18,166 --> 00:32:20,166
[music continues]

407
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,500
[music continues]

408
00:34:28,416 --> 00:34:30,416
[music continues]

409
00:35:39,208 --> 00:35:41,208
[music continues]

410
00:36:13,166 --> 00:36:15,166
[music ends]
